data.description: This fantastic house is move in ready and waiting for its new owners. Recently painted inside, the property boasts new LPV flooring on the lower level and recently installed carpeting upstairs. The generously sized primary bedroom offers a wonderful garden tub and a large walk-in closet. With two living rooms, one downstairs and one upstairs, there is plenty of space to relax and unwind. Moreover, the backyard is spacious and private, with a beautiful green space behind it and no neighbors. Washer & Drier included.
